{"word":"H2438 - חִירָם - Chîyrâm - khee-rawm' - Hiram","slug":"H2438","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">חִירָם</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>Chîyrâm"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>khee-rawm'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Hiram"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"Original: <b><he>חירם חירם</he></b> <p />Transliteration: <b>chı̂yrâm chı̂yrôm</b> <p />Phonetic: <b>khee-rawm'</b> <p class=\"bdb_def\"><b>BDB Definition</b>:</p> Hiram, Huram = \"noble\" <ol><li>the king of Tyre who sent workmen and materials to Jerusalem to build both the palace for David and the temple for Solomon</li><li>the chief architect and engineer of Solomon's temple sent by King Hiram to Solomon</li></ol> <p />Origin: another form of <a href=\"#/H2361\">H2361</a> <p />TWOT entry: None <p />Part(s) of speech: Proper Name Masculine "},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H2361\">H2361</a>, <a href=\"#/H251\">H251</a>, <a href=\"#/H256\">H256</a>, <a href=\"#/H257\">H257</a>, <a href=\"#/H260\">H260</a>, <a href=\"#/H264\">H264</a>, <a href=\"#/H267\">H267</a>, <a href=\"#/H269\">H269</a>, <a href=\"#/H277\">H277</a>, <a href=\"#/H279\">H279</a>, <a href=\"#/H281\">H281</a>, <a href=\"#/H282\">H282</a>, <a href=\"#/H283\">H283</a>, <a href=\"#/H284\">H284</a>, <a href=\"#/H285\">H285</a>, <a href=\"#/H286\">H286</a>, <a href=\"#/H287\">H287</a>, <a href=\"#/H288\">H288</a>, <a href=\"#/H289\">H289</a>, <a href=\"#/H290\">H290</a>, <a href=\"#/H291\">H291</a>, <a href=\"#/H292\">H292</a>, <a href=\"#/H293\">H293</a>, <a href=\"#/H294\">H294</a>, <a href=\"#/H295\">H295</a>, <a href=\"#/H296\">H296</a>, <a href=\"#/H297\">H297</a>, <a href=\"#/H298\">H298</a>, <a href=\"#/H299\">H299</a>, <a href=\"#/H300\">H300</a>, <a href=\"#/H301\">H301</a>, <a href=\"#/H302\">H302</a>"}]}